  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Patients older than 18 and under 75 years who have been undergone anterior resection
             of the rectum with sphincter preservation for rectal cancer

          -  Patients with LARS score &gt; 29

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Patient with intestinal inflammatory disease

          -  Patients with known irritable colon disease

          -  Pregnancy patients

          -  Patients with others intestinal resection segments different from the rectum

          -  Patients with metastatic disease

          -  Patient with previous history of posterior tibial neurostimulation or sacral nerve
             stimulation
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
